commit_list.message: Respect the X-Http-Method-Override header when choosing a handler.

RestPath.IsMatch should match a lowercase http method.

allowedVerbs is taken ToUpper so the httpMethod should also be ToUpper to
check for a match.
Failing razor test shows page is executed even though redirect was returned

Failing test for Html.CheckBoxFor() - cannot submit bool=true

Html.CheckBoxFor creates a second hidden input for the bool to ensure that
the false value is set with the post. But in the case of a true value,
both the checkbox and hidden input values are sent with the form.
ServiceStack sees this data as a list and has trouble deserializing the
list into a bool.
DefaultView failing test. Throws when req.Items["View"] doesn't exist.

Set a new expiration date when adding a permanent cookie.

Ultimately want to help ensure uniqueness of cookie name and expiration.

DeleteCookie should flow through the same path as AddCookie

This allows the expired cookie to get the correct domain value from
configuration at system.web/httpCookies

Facebook Provider - Handle an error callback

For example, the user decides to log in with facebook, but once at the
facebook permissions confirmation page chooses cancel.
Previously, facebook would callback and servicestack would return the user
to the facebook permissions confirmation page.
Now, the user is redirected back to the referrer url after choosing cancel.
